| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7266 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2951ca86-f3b0-5bfa-a6d0-06fb295ce205"
